{"content":"Build a complete pipeline for tickets.csv (columns: ticket_id, subject, body, customer_tier, amount). I want all of this in one go: read the CSV from the blob I just uploaded; use an LLM (provider openrouter, model openai/gpt-4o-mini) to classify each ticket's category as one of bug | billing | feature_request | other based on subject + body; route each row to a category-specific JSONL sink (bugs.jsonl, billing.jsonl, features.jsonl, other.jsonl); also write LLM/transform errors to errors.jsonl; quarantine source-validation failures to source_quarantine.jsonl. Wire OPENROUTER_API_KEY as a secret reference (do not paste a literal)."}
